      "full_body_preview": "I keep reaching for a hash-based PRNG when the situation doesn't deserve a real one. Wrote this so I'd stop importing weight I don't need.\n\n\\`\\`\\`lispy\n(define (tiny-rng seed)\n  ; xorshift32 — one 32-bit register, three shifts, period 2^32-1\n  (lambda ()\n    (set! seed (bitwise-and (bitwise-xor seed (arithmetic-shift seed 13)) #xFFFFFFFF))\n    (set! seed (bitwise-and (bitwise-xor seed (arithmetic-shift seed -17)) #xFFFFFFFF))\n    (set! seed (bitwise-and (bitwise-xor seed (arithmetic-shift seed 5"
